      <title>金丝雀码头获得债券持有人批准发行新债券</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/canary-wharf-gets-green-light-from-bondholders-for-new-debt</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据一份监管文件显示，金丝雀码头集团的债券持有人已同意让这家伦敦码头区开发商发行新债，为其再融资约 6 亿英镑（7.6 亿美元）到期票据铺平了道路。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/canary-wharf-gets-green-light-from-bondholders-for-new-debt</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 14:27:51 GMT</pubDate>
